State.Author: Grim Reaper
State.Description:
Some of you using TESALL tool might have noticed while generating landscape LODs that there are missing textures, probably due to ESP/ESM or meshes pointing to wrong texture directories.

3 textures from Vanilla Oblivion are missing :  chrock01.dds / terrainanvilgrass01.dds / terrainhdoblivionevilsymbol01.dds

This patch fixes those errors.
State.Name: TES4LL - Missing textures for Landscape LOD generation

State.Author: Elys
State.Description:
This OBSE plugin makes Oblivion play a 8 seconds duration silent voice for any missing voice file.



- If the subtitles are turned off, Elys_USV will force display subtitles for missing voice files.

- You will have up to 8 seconds to read long subtitles when there is no voice existing for an Oblivion plugin.

- Modder creating
State.Name: OBSE -Elys- Universal Silent Voice
